OL,3,CGuernsey government urged to tackle
OL,4,Chomelessness problem
OL,6,FJim Roberts, Director of the charity
OL,7,FAt Home in Guernsey, says: "It's
OL,8,Fextremely frustrating and I think this
OL,9,Fshould be a wake up call for the
OL,10,Fisland in many respects.
OL,12,F"Seeing visible evidence of rough
OL,13,Fsleeping is a canary in the mine
OL,14,Fbecause it points to other broader
OL,15,Fproblems around poverty and around the
OL,16,Flack of an adequate social safety net.
