OL,3,CGuernsey government urged to tackle
OL,4,Chomelessness problem
OL,6,F"They say you can judge the health of
OL,7,Fa society by how it treats it's most
OL,8,Fvulnerable and we can see how Guernsey
OL,9,Ftreats its most vulnerable and it is
OL,10,Fappalling.
OL,12,F"Should it call to the third sector to
OL,13,Fdo this? Surely a housed population is
OL,14,Fone of the central responsibilities of
OL,15,Fgovernment".
OL,17,FPaul Goddard took the below photo in
OL,18,FSt Peter Port bank and highlighted the
OL,19,Fsituation on social media, as he has
OL,20,Ffirst hand experience of being
OL,21,Fhomeless.
