OL,6,FPaul said: "I just felt saddened and I
OL,7,Fthink it's sickening to be fair. The
OL,8,Fguy looked like he was in his 60's".
OL,10,FSpeaking on how homelessness affects
OL,11,Fyou mentally, he added: "You wake up,
OL,12,Fyou're drained, exhausted. It's
OL,13,Fconstant stress and worry .
OL,15,F"Everyone deserves a place to live and
OL,16,Fcall home ` somewhere where they feel
OL,17,Fsafe and comfortable".
