OL,6,F"It's very frustrating that the
OL,7,FGuernsey Housing Association ran out
OL,8,Fof site early in this political term
OL,9,Fand that super-tanker has been taking
OL,10,Fa long time to turn around ` I think
OL,11,Fit is now starting to turn, we will
OL,12,Fsee far more affordable housing units
OL,13,Fbeing created in the next few years,
OL,14,Fbut this sort of dislocation in the
OL,15,Fprogramme should never be allowed to
OL,16,Fhappen again.
