OL,6,F"I would encourage anybody that finds
OL,7,Fthemselves genuinely homeless and out
OL,8,Fin the streets, or in lobbies or
OL,9,Fwhatever else, to go to Edward T
OL,10,FWheadon House. My staff ... will do
OL,11,Fwhatever we can to help".
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care said in a
OL,14,Fstatement: "St Julian's House has been
OL,15,Frunning at or near full capacity for
OL,16,Fabout three years now. There are
OL,17,Foccasions where we have vacant beds
OL,18,Fbut these are usually quickly filled.
